      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to exclude from certain minimum sentencing requirements a federal employee outside the United States who, while on-duty, uses, carries, or possesses an agency-issued firearm in a crime of violence.</p>]]></text>
